title: Tales of A Shinning Sword
description: Tales of A Shinning Sword Manhwa Eunho, the strongest in the yokai realm! He gained the chance to become a human being after losing the woman he loved and killing countless yokai. After passing the gate of reincarnation by accumulating merit for a thousand years to abandon his immortal body… He became a human being, held a sword, and learned martial arts for the first time. But this is very… easy? Biography of Hwiyeong Sword, 挥永剑�, 揮永劍傳, 휘영검전,Hwiyeong Geomjeon, Moonlight Sword Tales of A Shining Sword
